                      giv - The G(reat|tk|NU) Image Viewer
                   Dov Grobgeld <dov.grobgeld@weizmann.ac.il>

giv is an image and vector viewer based on the gtk_image_viewer
widget. It was designed especially with the scientific vision and the
computational geometry audience in mind and has support for drawing
vector graphics on top of the image.

Installation:

    * See INSTALL

Requirements:

    * gtk_image_viewer - See 
          http://imagic.weizmann.ac.il/~dov/freesw/gtk/gtk-image-viewer/

Documentation:

    * See doc/giv.html for documentation.
